{"tid":628484,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做姊妹撞返前男友，點知比佢....","createTime":"2018-04-14T02:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T03:30:15.000Z","uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c14f9c9d14eb2e07b9ae6b808234612dc8d50c","tid":628484,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:02:02.000Z","msg":"在三月的時份,參加朋友私婚宴,當天我是其中一個姊妹<br />\n當日穿了一件比較低胸,露了差不多三分之一胸部,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我感覺到有些賓客目光在我身上,這些都還好<br />\n<br />\n但人生有時候就那麼奇怪, 在當天我竟然碰到初戀男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n他主動跟我打招呼, 我們談了一陣子,然後我就忙我的<br />\n直到婚宴結束後,其他人開始收集東西搬走,<br />\n新娘房只剩下我,突然有人叩門,原來是他,<br />\n我們就進新娘房聊聊天,起初聊一些無聊話題,<br />\n到後來他講我們一起的經歷,當下心情有些忐忑,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n他慢慢靠近我身邊,講了一句&quot;其實我還喜歡你&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後親了我嘴唇,身體抖了一下<br />\n他開始摸我的胸,將我的裙子拉下來,<br />\n一邊摸胸,一邊親我的奶頭<br />\n身體已經被他搞到不行,下面妹妹開始出水<br />\n<br />\n我很快把他的肉棒放進口中,幫他口交<br />\n過了十幾分鐘,他忍不住在我口中噴發<br />\n最後我們在附近開了房間,那天晚上一共做了4次<br />\n全部射入小穴,感覺回到中學時時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本我不想給男友知道,但有一次給他發現我跟EX的聊天紀錄<br />\n男友很生氣,他接受不到我跟EX的事情,所以我們現在可以算是分開吧<br />\n<br />\n這段日子EX也有找過我,他無意間也表達對我意思<br />\n中間我們也有食飯,但沒有下一步事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6a5e6783afa125e3f064fc6016020a2a266b2c","tid":628484,"uid":150903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3acab1a3da3e5621ca3b3f2e219116d05e0c4798","tid":628484,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3651a92a9c74c683c5f7e5946853dbfce470d83b","tid":628484,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"劇情中途急進，甜分稍多<br />\n可於中線設下伏線交待過去<br />\n整體60分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c222f51e5579fd5ff22d00be9004b7fa2eb8f8b","tid":628484,"uid":18517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"臭G"},{"pid":"396f1dec71b7de7cdf106b841569c1a88b2a49bb","tid":628484,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:19:13.000Z","msg":"屌你收皮啦死GAY佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e4352a47f30c6e32630a5fa0577d80b64a84e7","tid":628484,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"又copy邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280197252a8ec5b8689da7857493601bde45bfe7","tid":628484,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:17:31.000Z","msg":"無是咁的，零分重作。"},{"pid":"eb67a7dff9711ca62202848c5c4f6dfca09d44fb","tid":628484,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"Gay佬又FF有撚含"}]}